  [Text] Beijing, 24 Jun (XINHUA) -- The Association for 
Relations Across the Taiwan Strait [ARATS] today sent a letter 
to the Taiwan Straits Exchange Foundation [SEF], proposing that 
the SEF organizes a group of news media leaders in Taiwan to 
visit the mainland at a time convenient to both sides in the 
second half of the year. 
  The letter says that, in accordance with the agreement 
reached during the talks between Wang Daohan and Gu Zhenfu [Ku 
