of visits between leaders and senior reporters of news media 
between the two sides. The letter also gave the views and 
suggestions of ARATS, after consultations with relevant 
departments, on matters stated in SEF's letters, dated 21 
February and 9 March respectively, about the itinerary, routes, 
and number of people in the visiting group. 

