<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    White House Undergoes Senior Personnel Changes </PHRASE></F></HT>
<H4>    Clinton Cited on Shifts </H4>

<F P=102> OW2706202694 Beijing XINHUA in English 1939 GMT 27 Jun 94 </F>
<F P=103> OW2706202694 </F>
<F P=104>  Beijing XINHUA </F>
